  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: SM Morning nar 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - The wind flows past me as the morning fog still hangs in the air.
  - THe sun has barely started to rise, an unnatural pink consuming the dark og night.
  - I reach the last sighting, approaching an old bridge.
  - An uneasy feeling washes over me.
  - Maybe this won't be so easy after all...
  - As I get closer, the feeling of uneasiness grows.
  - Something isn't right here.
  - Wait...
  - What's that in the distance?
  - A silhouette approaches. The faint outline of a woman.
  - She stops in front of me.
  line: 
